snippet.textDisplay: Very very mature stuff. Everything is on perfect spot. Those who are saying strings were best for coke studio, yes they brilliantly produced all the seasons and attracted so many types of audience to one platform but still they couldn't pull such soul in any of their tracks. This composition, vocals and arrangement is not piece of cake for anyone to produce. Kudos to Rohail Hayyat for such taste in music. I can totally relate to its vibe. Keep it up boss. You have a very matured fan base.
